    node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/health-command.spec.ts,null,project,240,targeted regression
  docs[3]{path,scope,note}:
    AGENTS.md,project,governing dogfood protocol
    PRD.md,project,hook lifecycle baseline update
    README.md,project,governing command contract
body: PRD milestone 5 still tracks broader hook call-site expansion. This task extends health storage checks to emit deterministic onRead hook events for history stream paths and validates with unit coverage.
